<section xml:id="the-execution-perspective" version="5.0" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
                                                      xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
                                                      xmlns:xl="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" >
  <title>The Execution Perspective</title>
  <para>
    In the Execution Perspective, you can see the following
    (<xref linkend="executionclient"/>):
  </para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        The Test Suite Browser
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        The Test Result View
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        The Properties View
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        The Image View
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  <figure xml:id="executionclient">
    <title>Execution Perspective</title>
    <mediaobject>
      <imageobject>
        <imagedata fileref="images/executionclient.png"/>
      </imageobject>
      <textobject><phrase>Execution
      Perspective</phrase></textobject>
    </mediaobject>
  </figure>
  <para>
    You cannot edit in the Execution Perspective, but you can see
    the results of tests that have been started interactively..
  </para>
</section>